data.description: Reduced for fast sale! Interest rates are coming down so don't wait. Sentrilock installed and READY TO SHOW! This is a classic Cape Cod-style home, 2BR, 1BA with a full basement, and a fully finished attic. Possibly could be set up as a 3BR with some creativity. The lot is large and encompasses the entire corner, with a city-maintained open area right across the street. Big, detached 2-car garage plus additional parking spaces next to the house. This is a fantastic location with a city-maintained park a few steps away. See the environmental video. Terrific pride of ownership in this spotless neighborhood. Check back shortly for Sentrilock info and use ShowingTime to show. Some historical images are available online (Zillow), and the home is basically unchanged. Low Indiana taxes, and a quiet lifestyle here. Information deemed reliable, not guaranteed.
